87
00:05:43,208 --> 00:05:44,125
Hey, Juiz?

88
00:05:44,208 --> 00:05:45,916
Yes?

89
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,541
Are you familiar with
the Johnny Hunter?

90
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:51,958
No... Would you like me
to do some research?

91
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:56,708
Nah... forget it.

92
00:05:56,791 --> 00:05:59,500
I've got it.

93
00:05:59,583 --> 00:06:02,500
Her real name is
Diana Kuroha Shiratori.

94
00:06:02,583 --> 00:06:04,666
She is the CEO of Monolom,

95
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,500
