for foreign models.

96
00:06:06,583 --> 00:06:08,125
Where is she right now?

97
00:06:08,208 --> 00:06:11,000
Location confirmed...

98
00:06:11,083 --> 00:06:12,583
She is currently
traveling by car

99
00:06:12,666 --> 00:06:15,041
in Minato near the main
Roppongi intersection.

100
00:06:15,125 --> 00:06:17,000
I bet that's right
near the hotel...

101
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:19,708
Juiz... I need you
to stop her for me.

102
00:06:19,791 --> 00:06:22,791
Is there a specific method
you'd like me to use?

103
00:06:22,875 --> 00:06:24,250
I don't care. The police...?

104
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:26,458
Whatever's the quickest, got it?

105
00:06:27,208 --> 00:06:29,458
Order received...
Noblesse oblige...

106
00:06:29,541 --> 00:06:31,916
Even though you are now
guilty of abusing state power,

107
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,000
I still pray for your
continuing service as a savior.

108
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,958
What's wrong, officer?
I was going the speed limit.

109
00:07:19,666 --> 00:07:20,625
Evening, ma'am...

110
00:07:20,708 --> 00:07:22,833
License and
registration, please.

111
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:46,875
Number Nine's trying
to make contact with me.

112
00:07:46,958 --> 00:07:52,208
But why? I feel... honored.

113
00:07:53,791 --> 00:07:59,916
Hey! Get back here!

114
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,083
Juiz.

115
00:08:01,166 --> 00:08:02,541
Find me the motorcycle
that went through

116
00:08:02,625 --> 00:08:05,625
the Kasumigaseki toll booth
about fifteen minutes ago.

117
00:08:16,791 --> 00:08:18,375
Hello? Takizawa?

118
00:08:18,458 --> 00:08:21,166
Saki... Your friend, Osugi...

119
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:22,416
I know where to find him.

120
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,916
Really...?

121
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,083
Takizawa figured out
where Osugi's being held.

122
00:08:27,166 --> 00:08:29,208
What, you're kidding...!
How'd he do that?

123
00:08:29,291 --> 00:08:30,791
Is he okay?

124
00:08:30,875 --> 00:08:35,083
He's in room 1109 of the
Hotel Insomnia in Roppongi...

125
00:08:35,166 --> 00:08:37,291
I'm just a few minutes
away from there...

126
00:08:37,375 --> 00:08:38,708
Talk to you soon.

127
00:08:38,791 --> 00:08:40,541
Hold on, don't hang up!

128
00:08:40,625 --> 00:08:42,125
Huh?

129
00:08:42,208 --> 00:08:43,541
Thanks for your help...

130
00:08:43,625 --> 00:08:45,625
