able to find him?

131
00:08:59,875 --> 00:09:01,500
Takizawa...?! What's wrong...?

132
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:02,875
Are you okay?

133
00:09:10,333 --> 00:09:14,541
Takizawa!
What happened...? Hello?!

134
00:09:44,791 --> 00:09:45,750
