the front desk...

137
00:09:50,916 --> 00:09:52,583
the guy said they're
just way too busy

138
00:09:52,666 --> 00:09:54,666
to send someone up to the room.

139
00:09:55,666 --> 00:09:58,041
Hey. Check this out.

140
00:09:59,333 --> 00:10:01,666
That's on the way to Roppongi!

141
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:07,583
There. Just try to get
into your hotel room now.

142
00:10:08,583 --> 00:10:10,375
If you wanna play dirty...

143
00:10:10,458 --> 00:10:15,791
Then, that's the way
we'll play it...!

144
00:10:29,583 --> 00:10:30,875
Uh, Miss Roppongi.

145
00:10:30,958 --> 00:10:32,500
I'm terribly sorry,
but the ownership

146
00:10:32,583 --> 00:10:34,541
of the hotel has
just changed hands.

147
00:10:34,625 --> 00:10:37,041
Unfortunately, we're
unable to grant access

148
00:10:37,125 --> 00:10:38,541
to the rooms at
this time, and uh...

149
00:10:38,625 --> 00:10:39,708
... and I'm afraid
I've been instructed

150
00:10:39,791 --> 00:10:41,916
to ask all guests to
vacate the premises.

151
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,750
I tried knocking on
the door to your room,

152
00:10:43,833 --> 00:10:45,833
but your companion
isn't answering...

153
00:10:45,916 --> 00:10:48,500
I... wasn't sure
if you would approve

154
00:10:48,583 --> 00:10:50,250
of me entering
the room by myself,

155
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:52,333
so I decided to wait for you.

156
00:10:52,416 --> 00:10:54,250
You made the right decision.

157
