It's too bad you have
to be the Supporter.

187
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,416
You're wrong.

188
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,500
I'm not the Supporter...

189
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:27,541
I'm just another Seleção...

190
00:13:27,625 --> 00:13:31,750
Plus... The only reason
I'm here is to save him.

191
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:33,666
He's a friend of
a friend of mine.

192
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,333
You're friends...

193
00:13:35,416 --> 00:13:38,000
with someone who knows
this degenerate lowlife?

194
00:13:38,083 --> 00:13:42,291
Well... from what I've heard
he's actually a stand-up guy...

195
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,833
Right, Osugi?

196
00:13:50,375 --> 00:13:51,750
Hey, easy!

197
00:13:55,708 --> 00:13:57,291
Let's assume for the
moment you actually

198
00:13:57,375 --> 00:14:00,041
are friends with
this piece of garbage.

199
00:14:00,125 --> 00:14:03,041
I will still have
my way with him.

200
00:14:04,625 --> 00:14:06,208
I feel my methods of mutilation

201
