are justified through
my personal convictions...

202
00:14:09,916 --> 00:14:13,375
I felt this way long before
I received this phone.

203
00:14:13,458 --> 00:14:15,916
Not even the
Supporter can stop me

204
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,833
from reaching my goal.

205
00:14:17,916 --> 00:14:20,375
I told you,
I'm not the Supporter...

206
00:14:20,458 --> 00:14:21,666
And how does a
serial killer come

207
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:24,416
into possession of a
Noblesse phone anyway?

208
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:25,291
