213
00:14:36,458 --> 00:14:38,750
Juiz gets rid of the bodies...?

214
00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:41,000
What in the world are
they talking about?

215
00:14:41,625 --> 00:14:42,666
What's up, Saki?

216
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:44,041
Did you get a hold of Takizawa?

217
00:14:45,125 --> 00:14:47,041
Uh-uh.

218
00:14:48,958 --> 00:14:50,375
I-I'm gonna go ahead on foot.

219
00:14:50,458 --> 00:14:51,708
See ya there!

220
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:55,500
Saki, wait!

221
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:59,541
I guess Seleção come from
all walks of life, huh...?

222
00:14:59,625 --> 00:15:02,291
You're so different
from Doctor Hiura...

223
00:15:02,375 --> 00:15:03,916
How do you expect
to win this game

224
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,125
if that's all you use Juiz for?

225
00:15:06,208 --> 00:15:08,458
For each pig I remove
from this earth...

226
00:15:08,541 --> 00:15:10,583
I use my agency to replace them

227
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:12,875
with a gentleman
from overseas...

228
00:15:12,958 --> 00:15:14,958
To be honest with you...

229
00:15:15,041 --> 00:15:17,333
I have no desire
to win this game...

230
00:15:17,416 --> 00:15:20,625
You can fight to change
the world all you want...

231
00:15:20,708 --> 00:15:22,125
but you'll never get more than

232
00:15:22,208 --> 00:15:24,500
half the world to
agree with your side.

233
00:15:24,583 --> 00:15:28,000
Until I exhaust the
last of my ten billion,

234
00:15:28,083 --> 00:15:31,208
I intend to carry out
my own brand of justice.

235
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:37,541
So in order for me
to get Osugi back...

236
00:15:37,625 --> 00:15:40,291
My only choice is to
take you out first.

237
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,583
I'm sorry I can't
be more accommodating.

238
00:15:43,666 --> 00:15:47,500
Remind me. Your name
is Kuroha, right...?

239
00:15:47,583 --> 00:15:48,208
I'm curious.

240
00:15:48,291 --> 00:15:49,375
What was it that got you

241
00:15:49,458 --> 00:15:53,000
into Johnny snipping
in the first place?

242
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,708
