243
00:15:56,791 --> 00:15:59,083
Yes, I do.

244
00:16:01,083 --> 00:16:02,541
Well there you go...

245
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:04,625
I'll have to save you, too...

246
00:16:04,708 --> 00:16:06,000
Cuz I'm different from you.

247
00:16:06,083 --> 00:16:08,708
See, I wanna win this game.

248
00:16:09,083 --> 00:16:12,458
Giving a serial killer the
chance to save the nation...?

249
00:16:12,541 --> 00:16:14,458
What has this
country come to...?

250
00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:16,166
This Mister Outside
deserves a beating

251
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:18,166
for the games he's playing.

252
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:22,125
Kuroha.

253
00:16:22,208 --> 00:16:26,166
You were hurt by a man
in the past, weren't you?

254
00:16:28,541 --> 00:16:30,333
And what makes you think that?

255
00:16:30,416 --> 00:16:33,750
I just get the feeling
that you've never...

256
00:16:33,833 --> 00:16:36,916
